		Example of typical distribution
		-------------------------------

\SRC 		  	Source of the LDG library (for example)
\DOC 		  	Documentation of the library
\INCLUDE\LDG	  	C header for application client
\LIB 		  	C library containing bindings for
			  	application client.
\GEMSYS\LDG    	The standard path to install the
			  	library,

README 		  	Instruction file
